import React from 'react'; import Title from '../../common/Title' import Description from '../../common/Description' import Image from '../../common/Image' const Technology = ({data}) => { return(
</div> <div className = "technology__subtitle"> <Description data = {data.subtitle} /> </div> <div className = "technology__image"> <Image {...data.image}/> </div> <div className = "technology__description"> <Description data = {data.description} /> </div> </section> ) } export default Technology;
